{"tid":1938720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國大爆發一日增九千確診，西班牙死亡率破6，意大利回落死六百人","createTime":"2020-03-22T17:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T02:02:01.000Z","uid":82002,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"bd67fbbb20ce21f07fa38d0f009a37dc7f306d88","tid":1938720,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T17:35:51.000Z","msg":"美國單日新增八千五百確診，<br />\n注意呢個數仲未封盤，<br />\n有可能破紀錄單日新增一萬。<br />\n不過好彩美帝醫療資源充足，<br />\n暫時死亡率都係1.6%左右<br />\n<br />\n意大利終於開始回落，<br />\n確診同死亡數字都減左少少，<br />\n但重症病例依然有幾千個，<br />\n難以稱得上過左最巔峰<br />\n<br />\n西班牙後起之秀開始殺上黎，<br />\n佢今日死亡率同確診大約等於一星期前意大利，<br />\n預計呢個禮拜西班牙會成為主角。<br />\n<br />\n其他地區，比利時，荷蘭，<br />\n葡萄牙，澳洲開始黎黎黎料，<br />\n確診個案大約15-20%咁加<br />\n<br />\n熱帶國家印尼死亡率迫近10%，<br />\n印度菲律賓泰國不斷確診，<br />\n證明個病去到夏天都唔會停。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LRsSTSY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLRsSTSY.png&h=2978036d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"155d391371de74ef4a8eb87812cb667378383860","tid":1938720,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T17:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係過萬左咩"},{"pid":"a2bcb3210b2dd7a64a15a7cd186a6fee31db68dc","tid":1938720,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"個網又入錯data 依家美國個數去番+7830"},{"pid":"3318aa59942f3d020c3e7124be845abb011aebbc","tid":1938720,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"155d391371de74ef4a8eb87812cb667378383860","tid":1938720,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T17:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係過萬左咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T17:41:22.000Z","msg":"應該就未"},{"pid":"ed6b8a78d6e2baebb7cc02066639b08108ad8a4e","tid":1938720,"uid":118120,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"美國d醫療貴到仆街<br />\n個死亡率可能會好高....